    REASON IV.  A fourth reason why all Christians should expect God to heal their sick bodies today is because the very same Holy Spirit who did all of Christ’s miracles and raised Him from the dead is still in the Church, and has all His old-time, life-giving power.
    In his fourth reason why all Christians should expect God to heal their sick bodies today, Dr. McCrossan finds his support in the Greek text of four words translated from the Textus Receptus (KJV) .  These are power (dunamis) , inf irmi-ties (astheneiais) , quicken (zoopeiesei) , and mortal (thneta).
